	<Title>
		Gallbladder cleanse: A &apos;natural&apos; remedy for gallstones?
	</Title>
	<Abstract>
		A gallbladder cleanse is a popular alternative remedy for gallstones. But does it work?
	</Abstract>
	<Question>
		What is a gallbladder cleanse? Is it an effective way to flush out gallstones?
	</Question>
